description: Preview the expected configurations of local connection.

commands.name: az connection preview-configuration app-insights
commands.summary: Preview the expected configurations of local connection to app-insights.
commands.syntax:
az connection preview-configuration app-insights [--client-type {dotnet, dotnet-internal, go, java, nodejs, none, python}]
                                                 [--secret]

commands.syntax:

                                              [--secret]
                                              [--service-principal]
                                              [--user-account]
